    <string name="help_directions">Playing Instructions:
    \n\t1. Select options from the drop-down menu on Main Screen
    \n\t2. Start the game and click on a tile to check whether a mine is present or not
    \n\t3. If no mine is present, the click will count as a scan.
    \n\t4. If a mine is present but is already revealed, the click will count as a scan and text will be displayed
    \n\t5. If a mine is not present, the click will count as a scan and text will be displayed
    \n\t6. Finish the game in minimum number of scans possible
    \n\n*Note: Game starts with default size of 4 X 6 and 6 Mines</string>
